      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted 2004 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine. This unit delivers linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. Critical preventative maintenance has been completed, including a ceramic IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced rear main seal. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, while the braking system utilizes four-piston monoblock calipers over ventilated rotors for consistent thermal management. Though showing minor stone chips indicative of road use, the paint retains excellent luster, and the interior leather displays minimal bolster wear. A high-performance driver\u2019s car ready for the canyons.",
